Programação pelo CSS

body {
  color: white;
  background-color: black;
font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;

  ul {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    list-style-type: none;
    padding: 16px;

     }

    a {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none

         }
        
       header img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 5px solid blue;
             }


    .center {
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
        color: blue;

 }

 footer img {
  width: 60px;
  height: 60px;
 }

 footer {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
 }

 footer a {
  margin: 30px;
  text-align: center
  ;

 }

 .container {
  padding: 0px 50px;
 }
nav a:hover{
  color: blue;
}
